，面试者去应聘应该是属于弱势群体，在职场打拼不如意想换个环境重新再来，面试很多家公司发现自己的不足，又是很致命却在短时间之内弥补不上，只能通过一些面试技巧来进行掩盖，太实诚了也不好。比如有面试者没研究过开源中间件，他可以看几遍文章熟记一个中间件，面试中就说了解一点某某中间件。","like_count":9,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1173080,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/e6/58/1c7f786a.jpg","nickname":"海飞","note":"","ucode":"C6B77418E1FB6D","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":439427,"discussion_content":"如果是您描述的这样和面试官说，我觉得没问题。\n你的确学了一些东西。\n在后面如何讲清技术一篇，我会说说技术的8个方面，这些方面，展示了不同的能力深度。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1550446647,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":67532,"user_name":"谭鹏","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1142009,"ip_address":"","ucode":"4A8120C4AA6F2F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/6c/f9/af80b4da.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1550193602,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"23914","content":"如果面试官不能让面试者感到尊重，这种公司会比较难以吸引到真正的优秀者。后面有涉及到如何了解团队的内容，会对这样的面试官小小地批评一下 :)","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"海飞","uid":"1173080","ctime":1550202289,"ip_address":"","comment_id":67532,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"31614964674","product_id":100023401,"comment_content":"有时面试，面试的人都不能称之为一个面试官,基本上就是一个开发人员，面试也根本不问什么价值观了，深度的技术问题，就是在例行公事，千篇一律的做个自我介绍，网上搜的题 问几个，再问些网上搜的问题，这面是感觉就像记流水账","like_count":7,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1173080,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/e6/58/1c7f786a.jpg","nickname":"海飞","note":"","ucode":"C6B77418E1FB6D","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":43923